In [251]:
x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test=train_test_split(x,y,test_size=0.3,random_state=10)
linear = LinearRegression()
linear.fit(x_train,y_train)
pred = linear.predict(x_test)
r2_score(y_test,pred)
